  <trk>
    <name>MUC-L1 — Bavarian Alps Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MUC and ride into the Bavarian Alps. Hit Garmisch-Partenkirchen — 700m and Deutsche Alpenstrasse — 1200m. Loop back to MUC over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
